<br>
 Since defensive is going to negate your damage so much anyways, DS's are a great way to still do damage while tanking.<br>
<br>
 It's possible somehow to stack multiple mage/druid DS's. I just haven't figured it out yet. I was up to like 112ds in Icewell once. Had 2 mage DS's on me, no idea how. <p><B><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6122>Grimmlokk</a>, Forlorn</B> <BR>
