<br>
In that case, only buff-slots really limit your max. DS. I can think of ~120 points worth of DS using 6 buff slots (not stacking druid/mage group/single ds, I still think this would be an exploit). DS's work great on unslowable mobs, but if the mob is slowable I'd rather use the slots for more AC or HP. <p><big><center>
